## Free Use

This license is FREE for:

1. **Personal use** — any individual for private, non-commercial purposes.
2. **Open-source projects** — any project whose source code is publicly available
   under an OSI-approved open-source license.
3. **Small commercial use** — any product or service whose total annual gross revenue
   (across all products and services offered by the same legal entity) is less than
   one million US dollars (USD $1,000,000) in the most recent twelve-month period.

---

## Commercial License Required

Any entity whose total annual gross revenue equals or exceeds USD $1,000,000 must
obtain a separate commercial license before using the Software in any product or
service that generates revenue.

Commercial license tiers:

- **Standard**: USD $299 per developer per year — for products below USD $10,000,000
  annual gross revenue.
- **Enterprise**: USD $10,000 per year (unlimited seats) — for products at or above
  USD $10,000,000 annual gross revenue or requiring a written license agreement.

To obtain a commercial license, contact: license@vexart.dev

